# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Root-level .npmignore
#
# This workspace root is PRIVATE and must never be published to npm.
# The publishable package lives in packages/react-smart-scheduler/.
#
# To publish the library:
#   cd packages/react-smart-scheduler
#   npm publish
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Block everything — this root should never be packed
*
